author: Ubisoft
description:
Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora - From the Ashes, coming December 19, 2025. 
Preorder today: https://ubi.li/2zc56

Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora™ – From the Ashes is an action-adventure expansion inspired by the new Avatar: Fire and Ash film.
Experience the ultimate Pandora adventure in the Western Frontier, with new third-person gameplay offering revamped combat and improved banshee mechanics. Use stealth or go guns blazing to seek vengeance and redemption against the invaders.

Pre-order now and get the Floating Mountains bonus content, including three different color patterns to customize your banshee and immerse yourself further in the Western Frontier.

Requires the base game to play.

Play as So’lek, a Na’vi warrior who has found solace with the Sarentu. Just as peace settles over the Western Frontier, a new threat rises: the RDA, now allied with the Ash clan, who are ruthless Na’vi bent on annihilation.
